{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_HAR_510.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x36,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hello. Sorry to intrude, but I come bearing good news!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Plus, I wanted to thank you, so just be excited for it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh...umm, thanks for what?<CR>Did I do something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xf5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ugh... Remember how you took part in my Thrilling Treasure Contest?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xf7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I was deeply impressed by the sparkle in your eyes and your pursuit of knowledge and reason."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "(W-Was I pursuing that much...?<CR>I kinda don't remember that.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb0,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "It's a special event that always draws many treasures, but it wasn't really popular with the general public."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb1,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "We've been having trouble finding enough participants, and I was starting to get impatient."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb1,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It's deplorable! Academically and historically rare items are presented from all over the world."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "However, make no mistake, you have the talent!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "With that being said, would you like to chase the mysteries that slumber in the ruin together!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Mysteries that slumber in the ruins...? Haha, I might be interested..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x56,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I also heard about the medicine you make from Marietta!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5e,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "It's our best selling product!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, I didn't know it was that popular..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I'm very happy that people are happy to use it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x58,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "O Ayesha, I need to express my appreciation somehow!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "However, I couldn't think of anything that you might be happy with."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I thought about money, but that's so inelegant. Then I came up with a great idea."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I actually manage an academically authoritative group."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "And as one of its members, I was thinking on presenting you with an amorphous gift!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "There's no need to hold back! As the chairman of the Ruins of Mystery Group, if you'd like..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I would like to present you with the title of an honorary member!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "A-An honorary member...<CR>Umm...that's okay."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, just okay? It's the highest honor an antique enthusiast can be awarded."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "No, that's not what I meant. Umm...I don't think...I need that title."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x141,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Wh-Wh-What!? You don't need this honor!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x143,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...it seems you are a much more interesting person than I thought."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "But this is troublesome. I wonder if there's anything else I can give you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I know, then let's do this!<CR>I think you'd accept this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "In a place reasonably close to this town, a ruin was discovered."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "It's a place where ancient glass artifacts were excavated, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "After digging up the ground, a ruin made of glass was discovered! Right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Regina?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb0,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Regina, I wanted to tell her that part."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hahaha, sorry. I just overheard you and couldn't resist."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "As a prospector, that's something I couldn't ignore."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "It's the same for me, too. I just can't sit still."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "However, I'm a busy man. So unfortunately, investigating it firsthand would be very difficult..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "So here it is. Ayesha, I'd like to ask you to investigate it for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Could you report to me the things you see and find at the ruin?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "For that information, I will pay you a handsome reward!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "It's a job? Then...I'm interested in that ruin, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "(If the ruin and Nio have any connection, I might be able to find some clues there.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then it's decided.<CR>I'm counting on you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, Harry, you like ruins, but you don't like dark, narrow places, do you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb0,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "Regina! I thought you promised you'd never bring that up!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "Didn't you come to see me about something? I'll talk to you over there, so just go and wait for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x19a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "Okay, got it. Well, I'll see you later, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "msg_string": "Ruins are treasure palaces for technology and knowledge. You might even be able to find something you like."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "msg_string": "Now, let me pay you a deposit.<CR>Please, accept it without reserve."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "msg_string": "You can go investigate whenever you can fit it in your schedule. I'll be waiting to hear back from you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x34,
            "msg_string": "(I don't know what I'll find,<CR>but I should just go there first.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You got 500 Cole."
        }
    ]
}